                
                PLANNER COMMAND SUMMARY

 general:

 (abtweak initial goal)  - invoke ABTWEAK
 (tweak initial goal)    - invoke TWEAK

 (cur)       show CURRENT planner settings, flags, expansions, etc.

 (show-dom)  show DOMAIN currently loaded (in Tweak format or AbTweak format)

 
 adjust planner settings:

 (ab-mode t/nil)     t changes mode to ABTWEAK, nil to TWEAK
 (debug-mode t/nil)  t causes display of expansion search space
 (rand-mode  t/nil)  t causes RANDOM selection of U p- goals to satisfy
 
 
 TWEAK - specific

 (sp-mode t/nil)     t causes SINGLE PRODUCER PROPERTY to be turned on

 ABTWEAK - specific

 (msp-mode weak/strong/nil)  set MONOTONIC SOLUTION PROPERTY indicator
 (prune-mode t/nil)          nil stops anyMSP pruning

 (td-mode t/nil)             t causes TOP DOWN PROPERTY pruning to occur
 (k-mode t/nil)              t causes *k-list* heuristic to be used


